<p>By example</p>  <pre><code>NSString *totoStr = @"toto toto toto-2 toto-3 toto"; </code></pre>  <p>My problem with wordwrapping and numberlines=0 , i get </p>  <blockquote>   <p>toto toto toto-<br>   2 toto-3 toto<br>   toto-4</p> </blockquote>  <p>I dont want separate this "toto-2" to next newline. I want consider like a full word like this output: </p>  <blockquote>   <p>toto toto<br>   toto-2 toto-3<br>   toto toto-4</p> </blockquote>  <p>Without any special character like "-" it's works.</p>  <p>Any idea how to do "linebreaking" correctly without using "\n" or "\r"</p>